id: pm-5teq
title: Warn on global service and renderer override footguns
description: "GitHub issue #96: registerService(\"output_format\") and registerRenderer overrides can silently replace output for every command, while extension doctor still reports the extension healthy. Duplicate check: pm search for service renderer override output_format corrupt output doctor warning found no open direct duplicate. Desired outcome: extension doctor/runtime should surface unsafe global override behavior and docs should explain pass-through/null fallback contracts."
